              <span id="reviewTextContainer290797248" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1945226533892546035">A re-read -- not quite as magical as when I read it in high school, but I am still a sucker for a) fantasy, b) sci-fi, c) origin stories and d) fictional worlds discovering their own origin stories (particularly that last one). Also a treat just having recently read <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/465904.Dragonsdawn' title='Dragonsdawn by Anne McCaffrey' rel='nofollow noopener'>Dragonsdawn</a>, since it echoes so nicely.</span>
  <span id="freeText1945226533892546035" style="display:none">A re-read -- not quite as magical as when I read it in high school, but I am still a sucker for a) fantasy, b) sci-fi, c) origin stories and d) fictional worlds discovering their own origin stories (particularly that last one). Also a treat just having recently read <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/465904.Dragonsdawn" title="Dragonsdawn by Anne McCaffrey" rel="nofollow noopener">Dragonsdawn</a>, since it echoes so nicely.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1945226533892546035" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


